{"tid":1570231,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵工會：破壞港鐵車站設施與示威者訴求無關","createTime":"2019-09-15T03:29:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T05:17:31.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"21f81ddcb7d93ed92a979e0039d4df4b7e451a63","tid":1570231,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:29:29.000Z","msg":"鐵路工會聯合會主席林偉強表示，近期示威中，港鐵員工被謾罵、起底感到心痛，又質疑破壞港鐵車站設施與示威者訴求無關。<br />\n<br />\n林偉強出席電台節目時稱，近日針對港鐵的示威中，對員工被人謾罵、起底、甚至襲擊，感到心痛及不公平，前線員工只是執行公司指令，將乘客安全運送到目的地。<br />\n<br />\n他質疑，衝擊港鐵車站與示威者訴求無關，港鐵車站的設施對示威者來說可能無感情，但實際上代表港鐵前線職員的精神，每當有設施受破壞，維修人員都會盡快修復，爭取翌日能維持服務。<br />\n<br />\n對於今年中秋節港鐵沒有提供通宵服務，林偉強表示，無通宵車對乘客十分不便，希望是最後一次。近日事件衝擊系統和同事，員工要求管方要保證同事乘客安全才落實通宵行車方案，同事對公司決定停止通宵服務都覺得無奈。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2250640/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2250640%2F&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=2ff340c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2250640/</a>"},{"pid":"7daa38f7abba1f600f726c90cecf78a1b611a6d8","tid":1570231,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be237cbdc7b4088727c62d79d480424830f9663","tid":1570231,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:34:47.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n第五期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1</a><br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/149